  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fling flying fans at your friends in chaotic multiplayer battles of up to 6 players! Grab spicy powerups, master snappy controls, and fight to be the last one standing in fast-paced rounds set in whimsical, hazard-filled arenas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/fe3b85c176f1cef4950c76b6fe305220.webp?t=1745353165\" width=501 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with up to 6 friends locally, add bots, or play online with Steam Remote Play. Dive into fast-paced free-for-all chaos where only one fighter emerges victorious! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/24e8086811b3cc8bef1b6c638729dd57.poster.avif?t=1745353165\" width=690 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/24e8086811b3cc8bef1b6c638729dd57.webm?t=1745353165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/24e8086811b3cc8bef1b6c638729dd57.mp4?t=1745353165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/43f0036a5baa64027fd9668e98a428dc.webp?t=1745353165\" width=501 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Matches feature multiple rounds lasting about 1 minute each for competitive rapid-fire play. Controls are easy to learn, yet snappy and responsive, providing depth and a high skill ceiling. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/2210eaac6dbac32799b070a31f825aea.poster.avif?t=1745353165\" width=690 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/2210eaac6dbac32799b070a31f825aea.webm?t=1745353165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/2210eaac6dbac32799b070a31f825aea.mp4?t=1745353165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/8957c5f0529dd2e5ff1ced9b0e5f7bcf.webp?t=1745353165\" width=501 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up round-exclusive powerups mid-battle: torch rivals with Fire Breath, freeze them solid with Ice Ring, transform foes with Mushroom Ring, or protect yourself with Earth Shield. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/662189e18220d5b33ecd41ad97355043.poster.avif?t=1745353165\" width=690 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/662189e18220d5b33ecd41ad97355043.webm?t=1745353165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/662189e18220d5b33ecd41ad97355043.mp4?t=1745353165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/27a3a4e8f58f39de3c046215f6a6e4df.webp?t=1745353165\" width=501 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate dynamic Asian-inspired arenas full of hazards - teleporters, fiery traps, giant mushrooms, and crushing stone hands that twist matches into unpredictable, wild battles.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/52d7f182335df88d14bb6a635e8932ca.poster.avif?t=1745353165\" width=690 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/52d7f182335df88d14bb6a635e8932ca.webm?t=1745353165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/52d7f182335df88d14bb6a635e8932ca.mp4?t=1745353165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/edf753534d0b61a2cc73972c7a70faa4.webp?t=1745353165\" width=501 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick your favorite from dim-sum inspired characters like HarGow the Shrimp Dumpling or BokBok the Bok Choy. They all play the same, but each have their own tasty style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/19d9ff8486b7b3b619809d96cbc12d1d.poster.avif?t=1745353165\" width=690 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/19d9ff8486b7b3b619809d96cbc12d1d.webm?t=1745353165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/19d9ff8486b7b3b619809d96cbc12d1d.mp4?t=1745353165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🪭 Quick, action-packed rounds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🥟 Deliciously cute dim sum fighters </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⛩️ Over 20 dynamic arenas with unique hazards </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧧 Round-exclusive  powerups </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 Easy controls, high skill ceiling  </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fling flying fans at your friends in chaotic multiplayer battles of up to 6 players! Grab spicy powerups, master snappy controls, and fight to be the last one standing in fast-paced rounds set in whimsical, hazard-filled arenas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/fe3b85c176f1cef4950c76b6fe305220.webp?t=1745353165\" width=501 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with up to 6 friends locally, add bots, or play online with Steam Remote Play. Dive into fast-paced free-for-all chaos where only one fighter emerges victorious! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/24e8086811b3cc8bef1b6c638729dd57.poster.avif?t=1745353165\" width=690 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/24e8086811b3cc8bef1b6c638729dd57.webm?t=1745353165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/24e8086811b3cc8bef1b6c638729dd57.mp4?t=1745353165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/43f0036a5baa64027fd9668e98a428dc.webp?t=1745353165\" width=501 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Matches feature multiple rounds lasting about 1 minute each for competitive rapid-fire play. Controls are easy to learn, yet snappy and responsive, providing depth and a high skill ceiling. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay mu