_paragraph\" >Navigate dynamic Asian-inspired arenas full of hazards - teleporters, fiery traps, giant mushrooms, and crushing stone hands that twist matches into unpredictable, wild battles.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/52d7f182335df88d14bb6a635e8932ca.poster.avif?t=1745353165\" width=690 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/52d7f182335df88d14bb6a635e8932ca.webm?t=1745353165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/52d7f182335df88d14bb6a635e8932ca.mp4?t=1745353165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/edf753534d0b61a2cc73972c7a70faa4.webp?t=1745353165\" width=501 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick your favorite from dim-sum inspired characters like HarGow the Shrimp Dumpling or BokBok the Bok Choy. They all play the same, but each have their own tasty style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/19d9ff8486b7b3b619809d96cbc12d1d.poster.avif?t=1745353165\" width=690 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/19d9ff8486b7b3b619809d96cbc12d1d.webm?t=1745353165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2862140/extras/19d9ff8486b7b3b619809d96cbc12d1d.mp4?t=1745353165\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><